[Term]
id: CIDER:0000049
name: pH fermented cider (1-14)
def: "Measured on a composite sample of fermented cider with a temperature compensating pH meter" []
is_a: CIDER:0000017 ! Variables
relationship: variable_of CIDER:0000050 ! fermented cider

